{"TopicId":224126,"ForumId":144,"TopicTitle":"Camera speed isn\u0027t scaled right between translation and rotation of the camera in capture mode [Not scaled accordingly]","CreatedByName":"Abelinoss","CreatedById":222638,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-15T14:34:26Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Abelinoss","CreatedById":222638,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-15T14:34:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.1 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003ESee modpack.\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, but I know 100% sure that this is also in stock because it has been this way since 0.1.0.0. It\u0027s a camera issue, the mods don\u0027t affect the camera system in any way. | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 11 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0AMD Ryzen 5 5600 6-core Processor | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0NVIDEA GeForce RTX 3060 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E15.91GB\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe rotation speed of the camera doesn\u0027t scale right with the translation. As a result you have to set your location on a very low camera speed. Increase the camera speed to change your rotation. Lower camera speed to fine-tune translation. and increase speed again to fine-tune rotation.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nThis is very annoying. They should be scaled in such a way that rotation and translation change is scaled properly.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdded video shows:\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nSpeed 1:\u003Cbr\u003E\n1. Normal speed translation\u003Cbr\u003E\n2. Too slow rotation (barely visible)\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nSpeed 2:\u003Cbr\u003E\n1. Normal speed rotastion\u003Cbr\u003E\n2. Too fast translation\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cvideo class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 controls=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.global.core.embeddedvideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Csource type=\u0022video/mp4\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/monthly_2024_03/KerbalSpaceProgram22024-03-1515-16-40.mp4.4f69db019b9ef930e740339a4041bce8.mp4\u0022\u003E\u003Ca class=\u0022ipsAttachLink\u0022 data-fileext=\u0022mp4\u0022 data-fileid=\u00221426\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/attachment.php?id=1426\u0026amp;key=076d3611d4f84d2dcc3ec833fb6e4496\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EKerbalSpaceProgram22024-03-1515-16-40.mp4\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/video\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/cfield.php?storage=form_Fields\u0026amp;path=modpak.ckan\u0026amp;fileKey=%5B!AES128GCM%5BoUtN8yQGrAOpaOTtdziIAZiav2AZ/QENPfh7jz09EJEYV1NHbt6AQTPfqAXSIE1aYYZrMcqBBq1vp8bM%5D%5B1d75b971f8c2ae8a00b40c47%5D%5Bd135dfcbc838eed904360c3cc7054b00%5D%5D\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Emodpak.\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003Eckan\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-03-16T19:42:36Z\u0022 title=\u002203/16/2024 07:42  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Mar 16\u0022\u003EMarch 16\u00